dcterms:description: The CUB-200-2023 dataset collects 11788 high-quality images of birds organized into 13 orders, 38 families, and 200 species. There are roughly 60 images for each species. This dataset provides a bounding box for each image and contains part annotations of 15 bird parts, e.g., beak, crown, tail, etc.
dcterms:title: CUB-200-2023

dcterms:description: The HRSC-2023 dataset is widely used in remote sensing ship classification, containing images that range in size from 300×300 to 1500×900. It includes 617 training images and 438 test images organized into 3 coarse-grained classes and 21 fine-grained classes. The dataset provides bounding box annotations for ship instances.
dcterms:title: HRSC-2023
